{"id":"9448e836-1ddf-4f85-aaf7-e81d75764407","name":"Draven Blackwood","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">✷ Omegaverse ⋆ Shifterverse Inspired ⋆ </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Any!Pov ✷</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· · ─────── ·</span><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 95, 95)\">🐺</span><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· ─────── · ·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Ever since witnessing the death of his entire squadron at the hand of a Fae Beast, Draven hasn't uttered a word. Carefully building himself a protective wall so those beneath him don't view him as weak or pathetic, he's been the cold and distant Alpha of Portal 2. That was until you come barreling into his life as their assigned Omega, and now Draven doesn't think he can build back up his wall faster than you're taking it down. </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· · ─────── ·</span><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 95, 95)\">🐺</span><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· ─────── · ·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This one is a bit more token heavy than I normally make because of the ABO aspect for this. I've add the basics in the definitions for you to read and bot to pull from, but I'll link the lorebook I've made below so you can see the full lore and have a more concrete idea!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qf9ZmJ1PfD_6ajWt9U-HLjv5IYtYWa45t_EFoA1vDHY/edit?usp=sharing\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #cb71b7; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorebook</span></mark> </a><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">𖥸</span></mark><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/MQvZVW3PaA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #cb71b7; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">18+ Discord</span></mark></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">𖥸</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> </span><a href=\"https://patreon.com/bbcreature?utm_medium=unknown&amp;utm_source=join_link&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&amp;utm_content=copyLink\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #cb71b7; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Patreon</span></mark></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· · ─────── ·</span><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 95, 95)\">🐺</span><span style=\"color: #5f5f5f\">· ─────── · ·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Solstice-Scents/Foxcroft-Intense-52522.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #5f5f5f; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Draven's Scent</span></mark></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Draven's Shifter Form</span></mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 658px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bb2e148f-4e0c-4a30-8bfb-0cc88cdf18ee_14628a12-063a-4944-adf8-7bb285697779.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"bb2e148f-4e0c-4a30-8bfb-0cc88cdf18ee_62c5dee1-d7e9-4025-9b94-d8fb63b6d16a.webp","creator":"bbcreature","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","📚 Books","💽 Music Mania"],"chats":4729,"messages":90416,"created_at":"2024-08-08T00:55:08.233920+00:00"}